name: ALIAXIN® LV - 2x1ml
description: JUVÉDERM® ULTRA 2 LIDOCAINE is an injectable filler, which is used to treat superficial to moderate facial lines and skin depressions, usually those around the lips and eyes. JUVÉDERM® ULTRA 2 LIDOCAINE contains hyaluronic acid, which is a natural substance found inside the human body. Its key property is to keep the skin hydrated whilst adding plumpness.  The product contains lidocaine to ensure a more comfortable injection.
